-------------
HOW TO DEPLOY
-------------

1.- Install wtdeploy:

    1.1.- workon your_virtual_env
    1.2.- pip install fabric
    1.3.- pip install -U -e git+git://github.com/ahmontero/wtdeploy.git#egg=wtdeploy

2.- Set your svn username and password in 'development' method at 'fabfile.py':
    env.repo_user = 'your_username'
    env.repo_password = 'your_password'

3.- cd project_root

4.- fab development push

5.- Install PDF tool at server:
	5.1.- Download wkhtmltopdf binary (i386 version even if the OS is 64-bits)      from http://code.google.com/p/wkhtmltopdf/downloads/list 
	5.2.- Assign permissions. 
	      Example: chmod +x /path/to/wkhtmltopdf
	5.3.- Set the binary path WKHTMLTOPDF_CMD at 'app_config.py'. 
		  Default path: '/usr/local/bin/wkhtmltopdf'
